data.description: Embrace the comfort and style of this four-bedroom, two-bathroom residence, nestled in the Sturbridge neighborhood.  As you step inside, the warmth of the hardwood-floored foyer welcomes you, seamlessly transitioning into an open-plan dining area and a cozy living room with patio access, which promises an ideal setting for both entertaining and quiet evenings at home.  The spacious eat-in kitchen, which features stunning granite countertops, a gas cooktop, ample pantry space, and a convenient work island.  This home features new light fixtures and light switches.  Flexibility is key, with the first hallway bedroom featuring elegant French doors, perfectly suited for use as a bedroom or home office.  Down the hall, two additional bedrooms and a well-appointed bathroom with new toilets accommodate family and guests with ease.  The main suite serves as a private sanctuary, with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual sinks however it wouldn’t be complete without the walk-in closet with an organized system.  The laundry room leading to a double garage is equipped with a utility sink.  Modern conveniences such as smart key locks and the installation of fiber optic cable, ensuring high-speed internet connectivity that meets today's digital demands.  The neighborhood amenities are a clubhouse, pool, & tennis courts. Conveniently located close to dining, shopping, hospital, and the interstate.
